                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tavern Challenge: Friendly Fracas - The Emperor of Fire and Iron Tolls the Bell",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow.\" \"A cat friend of mine who travels with humans told me that huge crabs live on the beaches of Fontaine, and the sound of their leader clicking its claws is like the clamorous tolling of a bell...\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: The Emperor of Fire and Iron is immune to Frozen, Stun, and Petrification, and when it uses Elemental Bursts, it will gain 3 Armored Crab Carapace stacks. When the Action Phase begins, if the Emperor does not have Armored Crab Carapace equipped, it will gain 3 stacks of said Carapace.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
